cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CY 

This paper belongs to the arXiv CS sub-category of natural language processing (NLP) and information retrieval (IR) as it deals with the identification of opinion polarity in customer reviews. Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which are commonly used in the sub-categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, since the paper deals with Web information extraction, it could also be classified under cs.CY (Computers and Society).
